snippet.title: Assetto Corsa Competizione Gameplay Lamborghini Huracàn GT3 @ Misano - Puddles Tech Demo
snippet.description: Kunos Simulazioni recently attended the Blancpain GT Series weekend in Misano World Circuit to showcase gameplay footage of Assetto Corsa Competizione. This video shows the 2/4 special event in Misano, featuring the Lamborghini Huracàn GT3 in action on track with mixed dry/wet surface. For more information, visit www.assettocorsa.net/competizione
